3. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper uses genetic algorithms to approximate the weight enumerator, which is a numerical analysis technique. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper involves finding the weight enumerator of codes that are stable under certain groups, which is a topic related to systems and control. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - The paper involves using genetic algorithms to solve a linear system of integer variables, which can be a computationally complex task.
